sentences.english: The paper also reports some data about sexual maturity, reproduction rate, etc.
sentences.chinese: 此外，本文还报导了一些有关性成熟和产羔率等资料。

sentences.english: They reach sexual maturity only at age 20 to 30.
sentences.chinese: 他们达到性成熟仅仅需要20年至30年。

sentences.english: Small breeds tend to mature faster than large breeds.
sentences.chinese: 小型犬达到性成熟的年龄一般比大型犬小。

sentences.english: Even then, they only lay eggs about every five years.
sentences.chinese: 即便性成熟了，它们也是每隔五年才产卵一次。

sentences.english: The sexual maturation experiences four stages.
sentences.chinese: 雄体的性成熟一般经历四个龄期。

sentences.english: The factors of influence on the living sexually mature of Dugesia sp. were discussed in the article.
sentences.chinese: 本文对影响三角涡虫性成熟的因素也进行了讨论。

sentences.english: The histology of pituitary gland from sexually matured female mandarin fish was studied.
sentences.chinese: 对性成熟雌性鳜鱼的脑垂体进行了组织学研究。

sentences.english: Ferret's sexual maturity is reached between 5 and 6 months.
sentences.chinese: 雪貂在出生后5到6个月达到性成熟。

definition: the breeding season (zool.)/oestrus (period of sexual receptivity of female mammals)
to give birth (animals)/to bear a litter
the young (unborn or newborn) of an animal/larva
